AtoMail ChangeLog
-----------------

See Git history for recent developments.

0.10
- Force preformatted display of text-only entries.

0.9
- Fixed timezone handling

0.8
- Fixed outstanding issues with encodings
- Fixed problem with timezone conversion (Thanks to Carl Duisberg)

0.7
- Trim spaces from subject prefixes

0.6
- Handle recursive multi-part messages correctly
- Allow messages without contents

0.5
- Give HTML messages priority
- Fix incorrect check for already existing messages in feed
- Simplify message retrieval
